Two Pakistani male besties who fell in love with the same girl and have now decided to share by sleeping with the same girl without fighting each other. One of the men, with the handle, @bazilkhann took to Twitter to make the relationship public and shared a photos of his girlfriend which he claims he shares with his male bestie. The besties can be seen kissing the same girl in the picture. He wrote: “My best friend and I love the same girl, we don’t fight, we come to an agreement because that’s what friendship is all about. My best friend and I love the same girl, we don't fight, we come to an agreement because that's what friendship is all about. pic.twitter.com/T8iBaHTYEF Source